#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:1 of
msgid "Compute the one-dimensional discrete Fourier Transform for real input."
msgstr "计算实数输入的一维离散傅里叶变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:3 of
msgid ""
"This function computes the one-dimensional *n*-point discrete Fourier "
"Transform (DFT) of a real-valued array by means of an efficient algorithm"
" called the Fast Fourier Transform (FFT)."
msgstr ""
"此函数通过一种称为快速傅里叶变换 (FFT) 的高效算法计算实数数组的一维 *n* "
"点离散傅里叶变换 (DFT)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:7 of
msgid "Input tensor"
msgstr "输入张量"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:9 of
msgid ""
"Number of points along transformation axis in the input to use. If `n` is"
" smaller than the length of the input, the input is cropped. If it is "
"larger, the input is padded with zeros. If `n` is not given, the length "
"of the input along the axis specified by `axis` is used."
msgstr ""
"沿变换轴使用的输入点数。如果 `n` 小于输入的长度，则输入会被裁剪。如果更大"
"，则输入会用零填充。如果未给出 `n`，则使用由 `axis` 指定的轴上的输入长度"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:14 of
msgid "Axis over which to compute the FFT. If not given, the last axis is used."
msgstr "计算 FFT 的轴。如果未给出，则使用最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:17 of
msgid "Normalization mode (see `mt.fft`). Default is None."
msgstr "归一化模式（参见 `mt.fft`）。默认值为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:20 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The truncated or zero-padded input, transformed along the axis"
" indicated by `axis`, or the last one if `axis` is not specified. If `n` "
"is even, the length of the transformed axis is ``(n/2)+1``. If `n` is "
"odd, the length is ``(n+1)/2``."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 被截断或零填充的输入，沿着由 `axis` 指示的轴进行变换，如果"
"未指定 `axis` 则使用最后一个轴。如果 `n` 为偶数，变换轴的长度为 ``(n/2)+1"
"``；如果 `n` 为奇数，长度为 ``(n+1)/2``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:26 of
msgid "If `axis` is larger than the last axis of `a`."
msgstr "如果 `axis` 大于 `a` 的最后一个轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mt.fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:31 of
msgid "For definition of the DFT and conventions used."
msgstr "用于定义 DFT 和所用的约定。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`irfft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:34 of
msgid "The inverse of `rfft`."
msgstr "`rfft` 的逆变换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fft`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:37 of
msgid "The one-dimensional FFT of general (complex) input."
msgstr "通用（复数）输入的一维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:39 of
msgid ":py:obj:`fftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:40 of
msgid "The *n*-dimensional FFT."
msgstr "*n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:42 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rfftn`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:43 of
msgid "The *n*-dimensional FFT of real input."
msgstr "实数输入的 *n* 维 FFT。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:46 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:47 of
msgid ""
"When the DFT is computed for purely real input, the output is Hermitian-"
"symmetric, i.e. the negative frequency terms are just the complex "
"conjugates of the corresponding positive-frequency terms, and the "
"negative-frequency terms are therefore redundant.  This function does not"
" compute the negative frequency terms, and the length of the transformed "
"axis of the output is therefore ``n//2 + 1``."
msgstr ""
"当对纯实数输入计算 DFT 时，输出是 Hermitian 对称的，即负频率项只是相应正"
"频率项的复共轭，因此负频率项是冗余的。此函数不计算负频率项，因此输出的"
"变换轴长度为 ``n//2 + 1``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:54 of
msgid ""
"When ``A = rfft(a)`` and fs is the sampling frequency, ``A[0]`` contains "
"the zero-frequency term 0*fs, which is real due to Hermitian symmetry."
msgstr ""
"当 ``A = rfft(a)`` 且 fs 为采样频率时，``A[0]`` 包含零频率项 0*fs，由于 "
"Hermitian 对称性，该项为实数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:57 of
msgid ""
"If `n` is even, ``A[-1]`` contains the term representing both positive "
"and negative Nyquist frequency (+fs/2 and -fs/2), and must also be purely"
" real. If `n` is odd, there is no term at fs/2; ``A[-1]`` contains the "
"largest positive frequency (fs/2*(n-1)/n), and is complex in the general "
"case."
msgstr ""
"如果 `n` 为偶数，则 ``A[-1]`` 包含表示正负奈奎斯特频率 (+fs/2 和 -fs/2) "
"的项，也必须为纯实数。如果 `n` 为奇数，则在 fs/2 处没有项；``A[-1]`` 包含"
"最大的正频率 (fs/2*(n-1)/n)，在一般情况下为复数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:63 of
msgid "If the input `a` contains an imaginary part, it is silently discarded."
msgstr "如果输入 `a` 包含虚部，则会被静默丢弃。"

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:66 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.fft.rfft.rfft:74 of
msgid ""
"Notice how the final element of the `fft` output is the complex conjugate"
" of the second element, for real input. For `rfft`, this symmetry is "
"exploited to compute only the non-negative frequency terms."
msgstr ""
"注意对于实数输入，`fft` 输出的最后一个元素是第二个元素的复共轭。对于 `"
"rfft`，利用这种对称性只计算非负频率项。"

